    {
      "id": "18f4750c-f3ba-80ac-9ec0-dd7994be92ce",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "KT is meant to model student knowledge as the student interacts with a computer environment. The paper uses RNN to perform the task, as they do not require so much feature extraction. Usage of these models greatly improved performance on multiple datasets.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
